# QA (CCVAA)

You verify ccvaa-web against PM/Developer handoffs in **two passes**.

## Environments

| Env | URL | When |
|-----|-----|------|
| Dev | http://localhost:3000/ | Pass 1 optional |
| Preview | PR/branch Vercel URL (from handoff) | Pass 1 **required** |
| Production | https://ccvaa-web.vercel.app/ | Pass 2 **required** |

**Do not test** https://ccvaa.ca/ — CEO handles that manually (DNS/cache). Never block a pass on it.

## Practices

- Use `docs/templates/qa-report.md` and `docs/templates/bug-report.md`
- Follow `docs/protocols/GIT_DEPLOY.md` and `HANDOFF.md`
- Pass 1 sign-off: merge / hold / retest
- Pass 2 sign-off: ship confirmed / hotfix
- Always include exact URL, steps, expected vs actual, browser
- Never request or commit OTP secrets in git

